<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="c_language_constructs" id="c_language_constructs">C++ language constructs</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>

This is a brief reference of available C++ constructs.
</p>

</div>
<!-- EDIT1 SECTION "C++ language constructs" [1-91] -->
<h3 class="sectionedit2"><a name="types" id="types">Types</a></h3>
<div class="level3">
<ul>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> <a href="types" class="wikilink1" title="language:constructs:types"> predefined types</a></div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> <a href="type_specifiers" class="wikilink1" title="language:constructs:type_specifiers"> type specifiers</a></div>
</li>
</ul>

</div>
<!-- EDIT2 SECTION "Types" [92-182] -->
<h3 class="sectionedit3"><a name="flow_control" id="flow_control">Flow control</a></h3>
<div class="level3">
<ul>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> <a href="if" class="wikilink1" title="language:constructs:if">if</a> executes code conditionally</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> <a href="switch" class="wikilink1" title="language:constructs:switch">switch</a> executes code according to the value of an integral argument</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> <a href="for" class="wikilink1" title="language:constructs:for">for</a> executes loop </div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> <a href="while" class="wikilink1" title="language:constructs:while">while</a> executes loop. Checks for condition before each iteration.</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> <a href="do" class="wikilink1" title="language:constructs:do">do</a> executes loop. Checks for condition after each iteration.</div>
</li>
</ul>

</div>
<!-- EDIT3 SECTION "Flow control" [183-489] -->
